ana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">They nerfed the dang boards. The forums on the main EQ site are gone and are now moderated.<br>
