Herder.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uprocax.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Procax</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>80</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/29/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>11:42:22 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I never said people didnt care, im sure some of the lame trollers cared quite pasionately about their lame little pet issues like making necro pets the way they were in 99 or some shit.  'Caring' isnt nessessry or sufficent for 'useful' however^^  Im sure the well written posts will have no problems making it by moderation, and the rest of the crap was just that.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#212141><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uherdervazaelle.showPublicProfile?language=EN>HerderVazaelle</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>50</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/29/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>12:11:32 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I went to the boards and looked, the posts are all &quot;Thanks for making the boats announce&quot; and generally benign issues such as that.<br>
<br>
There were many issues being debated on gameplay at the time of its demise:<br>
<br>
PvP issues<br>
-X teaming<br>
-Deleveling<br>
-Zone Ganking<br>
-Team Balance<br>
-Corpse Camping<br>
<br>
Balance Issues<br>
-High level encounters only needing war/cler/rogue<br>
-Resists in Velious<br>
-INT caster uselessness<br>
-Complete Heal/Rez Issues<br>
<br>
<br>
Stealth Nerfs<br>
-Bind Sight<br>
-That shield thingy (heh, forgot the name)<br>
<br>
Outright Nerfs<br>
-Cleric BP's<br>
<br>
Customer Service<br>
-Epic creatures poofing when dotted and caster goes LD<br>
-Epic Reward Poofing if no open slot in inventory <br>
-Name changes (some are warranted but where they going to go now?)<br>
<br>
