<br>
I don't hink this was a good move. Seriously..yeah..alot of crap there and some heavy handed moderation was in order, but there still were alot of legitimate items there.  And with those items comes alot of information.<br>
<br>
I'm of the firm belief that all the messages they get now will be full of fuzzy pink clouds and snow white bunnies.  A much better facade to appease the parent company..&quot;See?  Everyone is happy with the game and here is your cheque&quot;<br>
<br>
Besides...everyone is going to be posting all over the place now, and no consolidated position to work from.  Divide and conquer.<br>
<br>
Or at least Divide and everything 'appears' to be all good in the world.....<br>
<br>
</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#212141><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/ucaetlynlifebringer.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Caetlyn Lifebringer</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>1</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/29/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>2:16:47 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Herder, were you really reading the same boards I was?<br>
<br>
