Caet</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/uprocax.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Procax</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>81</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/29/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>2:47:25 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Look at the items you listed that had been fixed.  If they had all stayed broken about 1% of the population would have cared, honestly.  I know you are gonna point to alchemy, but I dont think that every shaman cared that much.  I think that when people got to the board, and started to stew about it, it became_ a big issue for them, I bet if, for example, everquest was totally unsupported by patches, like a console game or something, and say alchemy didnt work, close to 100% of the people who play now still would.  On the other hand, look at the 100s of harmful_, balance destroying_, partisan_ suggestions that were posed and massively bumped every single day.  I think its a damn good thing they didnt listen to us more.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#212141><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/utrinityfirestrike.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Trinity Firestrike</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>35</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/30/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>5:31:09 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Petitions stay in the GM/guide que for 3hrs, even if you log or goto chat or whatnaught.  Course, if youre not online for like 5-10min after a guide pulls the pet, he/she will delete it or make a note in his/her log to post it.</font><P><P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#2F2F4F><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub41.ezboard.com/usllackblader.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sllack Blader</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://24.221.41.117:8080/images/adder65.jpg BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>108</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>3/30/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#ffffff>8:23:29 am</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT><BR><img src=http://24.221.41.117:8080/images/adder65.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re: The Nerf to end all nerfs</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">I agree with what Herder said...<br>
